   - Code in language/ → MIT (dual copyright)
   
   You may freely use, modify, and distribute the CODE under those licenses.
   This spec license does not restrict code usage in any way.

4. RATIONALE
   Specifications represent significant design investment. This license
   prevents competitors from copying specs to build competing products
